{"tid":1967537,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：如確診數字持續回落 極可能5月底復課","createTime":"2020-04-11T04:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T04:49:21.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37f7310e3391ab1f857cf3d4e3885713c4cb388e","tid":1967537,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"距離4月24日中學文憑試（DSE）開考不足兩周，教育局長楊潤雄昨稱，如確診個案數字持續回落，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4月24日<span style=\"color: red;\">如期開考機會非常大。他回應是否待完成所有文憑試筆試，即5月底才可復課時，表示「極有可能最後會是這樣」</span></span></span></strong>，但不想抹殺所有可能，若文憑試如期開考，會視乎疫情發展再決定。消息稱，學界曾與局方商討，料最早復課日為文憑試筆試之後。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，約有20多個試場考試期間有近400名考生應考，學界曾向局方反映擔憂，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">商討後料最早復課日為文憑試筆試之後，屆時或高中先復課</span></span></strong>他補充，學界對何時復課、如何復課、誰復課未有統一方案，認為如5月底復課，教育局須提供清晰指引，「如高中先復課，初中又網上教學，老師會否疲於奔命？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2993002950759820/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F498203090239831%2Fposts%2F2993002950759820%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479Vc%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=2c8f9b0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/498203090239831/posts/2993002950759820/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"5089e0ed5d180b32508b58e33a57e4a7ab3c14fe","tid":1967537,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f19220234b969143d0612c3d465a88c9255ddc0","tid":1967537,"uid":291947,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:25:09.000Z","msg":"唔想復課，又要7點起身。。。"},{"pid":"35a70af6adf5ecdbb40402119f9d9c6f4125b686","tid":1967537,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"其實政府都係燈神，  大家預期嚟緊會有大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"